	(text_box "Simple board to break out any 5-to-8 pin DIN socket.\n\nI've been using Deltron 671-0x01 series (or similar) as the same 8-pin footprint works for multiple sockets:\n671-0501 = 5-pin DIN\n671-0601 = 6-pin DIN\n671-0701 = 7-pin DIN\n671-0801 = 8-pin DIN\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
